<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#fafaf7">
<title>{{ hero_title_line1 }} · ISSUE #{{ issue_number }}</title>
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }
html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body {
  font-family: "Charter", "Merriweather", "Noto Serif KR", Georgia, serif;
  background: #fafaf7;
  color: #242424;
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.68;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  letter-spacing: 0;
  /* 플로팅 네비 공간 확보 */
  padding-bottom: calc(80px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
}
a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
a:active { opacity: 0.6; }

.app { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

/* 상단 바 */
.bar {
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  padding: calc(16px + env(safe-area-inset-top)) 0 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e6df;
}
.bar .brand { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
.bar .brand::before { content: "■ "; color: #1a8917; }
.bar .edition { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #6b6b6b; }

.intro { padding: 40px 0 32px; text-align: center; }
.intro .greeting {
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #1a8917; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.intro h1 {
  font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  margin: 0 0 14px;
}
.intro .sub { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #6b6b6b; }
.intro .meta {
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px; color: #999; margin-top: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.intro .meta::before { content: "—— "; }
.intro .meta::after { content: " ——"; }

.hashtags {
  text-align: center; padding: 8px 0 24px;
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;
}
.hashtags span {
  display: inline-block; margin: 4px 6px;
  color: #1a8917; font-weight: 600;
}

/* 섹션 */
section.feed-sec { scroll-margin-top: 20px; }

.sec-divider {
  text-align: center; padding: 50px 0 24px;
  position: relative;
}
.sec-divider::before {
  content: ""; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 1px; background: #e6e6df;
}
.sec-divider h2 {
  display: inline-block; position: relative;
  background: #fafaf7; padding: 0 20px;
  font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin: 0;
}

/* 스토리 카드 */
.story {
  display: block; padding: 28px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e6df;
}
.story:active { opacity: 0.6; }
.story:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }

.story .head {
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px; color: #6b6b6b;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
}
.story .head .src { font-weight: 700; color: #242424; }
.story .head .dot { color: #c5c5c5; }

.story h3 {
  font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.22; letter-spacing: -0.018em;
  margin: 0 0 10px;
  color: #242424;
}

.story .lede {
  font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.55;
  color: #4a4a4a; margin: 0 0 14px;
}

.story .foot {
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  font-size: 13px; color: #6b6b6b;
  flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px;
}
.story .foot .read { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
.story .foot .read::before { content: "📖"; }

/* 기사 키워드 해시태그 */
.story .keywords {
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  margin-top: 12px;
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px;
}
.story .keywords span {
  background: #f2f2ed;
  color: #1a8917;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* 중요도 pill — 점수별 색 스케일 (v3) */
.score {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
  padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 800;
  font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  min-height: 24px;
  position: relative;
}
.score::before { content: "★"; font-size: 10px; }

/* 9.0+ — 최고 등급: 그라디언트 + 더블 링 + 글로우 펄스 + 🔥 */
.score-vhigh {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #991b1b 0%, #dc2626 50%, #f59e0b 100%);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 5px 13px;
  font-size: 12.5px;
  font-weight: 900;
  box-shadow:
    0 0 0 2px #fafaf7,
    0 0 0 4px #991b1b,
    0 4px 14px rgba(153, 27, 27, 0.55);
  animation: glow-vhigh 2.2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.score-vhigh::before { content: "🔥"; font-size: 11px; }
@keyframes glow-vhigh {
  0%, 100% {
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 2px #fafaf7,
      0 0 0 4px #991b1b,
      0 4px 14px rgba(153, 27, 27, 0.55);
  }
  50% {
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 2px #fafaf7,
      0 0 0 5px #dc2626,
      0 6px 22px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.8);
  }
}

/* 8.5+ — 매우 높음: 파스텔 초록 */
.score-superhigh {
  background: #86efac; color: #14532d;
  border: 1px solid #4ade80;
}

/* 8.0+ — 높음: 파스텔 노랑 */
.score-high {
  background: #fde68a; color: #713f12;
  border: 1px solid #facc15;
}

/* 7.0+ — 중상: 파스텔 시안 */
.score-midhigh {
  background: #cffafe; color: #0e7490;
  border: 1px solid #a5f3fc;
}

/* 5.0+ — 중간: 파스텔 라벤더 */
.score-mid {
  background: #e0e7ff; color: #3730a3;
  border: 1px solid #c7d2fe;
}

/* 3.0+ — 낮음: 파스텔 민트 */
.score-low {
  background: #dcfce7; color: #14532d;
  border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
}

/* <3.0 — 매우 낮음: 연회색 */
.score-vlow {
  background: #f3f4f6; color: #9ca3af;
  border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
}

/* Top story */
.top-story {
  padding: 32px 0 40px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e6df;
}
.top-story .kicker {
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #c2410c; margin-bottom: 12px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.top-story h2 {
  font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em;
  margin: 0 0 14px;
}
.top-story .by {
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: 14px; color: #6b6b6b;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  padding-bottom: 20px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e6df;
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; align-items: center;
}
.top-story .body {
  font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.68;
}
.top-story .body::first-letter {
  font-size: 64px; float: left;
  line-height: 0.85; margin: 8px 12px 0 0;
  font-weight: 700; color: #1a8917;
}
.top-story .keywords {
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  margin-top: 20px;
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px;
}
.top-story .keywords span {
  background: #f2f2ed; color: #1a8917;
  padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 600;
}

/* 인사이트 레이어 — <details> 토글 */
.why-insights {
  margin-top: 20px;
  background: #f7f7f2;
  border: 1px solid #e6e6df;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
}
.why-insights[open] { padding-bottom: 18px; }
.why-insights > summary {
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #1a8917;
  list-style: none;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  min-height: 32px;
}
.why-insights > summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
.why-insights > summary::after {
  content: "▾"; transition: transform 0.2s;
  font-size: 14px; color: #6b6b6b;
}
.why-insights[open] > summary::after { transform: rotate(180deg); }

.why-insights .axis {
  margin-top: 14px; padding-top: 14px;
  border-top: 1px dashed #d6cdbb;
}
.why-insights .axis:first-of-type { border-top: none; padding-top: 4px; }
.why-insights .axis .axis-title {
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: #242424;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
}
.why-insights .axis .axis-title .icon { font-size: 16px; }
.why-insights .axis .axis-body {
  font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.55; color: #3a3a3a;
}

/* 뒤로 / footer */
footer {
  padding: 50px 0 30px;
  text-align: center;
  font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: 12.5px; color: #6b6b6b;
  border-top: 1px solid #e6e6df;
  margin-top: 40px;
}
footer .disclosure {
  color: #6b6b6b; font-size: 12px; max-width: 520px;
  margin: 0 auto 14px; line-height: 1.6;
}
footer .issue { font-weight: 800; color: #242424; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
footer .sources {
  color: #999; font-size: 11.5px; line-height: 1.8;
  margin-top: 8px;
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
/* 플로팅 섹션 네비게이션 (고정)            */
/* ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
.floating-nav {
  position: fixed;
  left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  bottom: calc(14px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
  z-index: 30;
  display: flex; gap: 4px;
  padding: 5px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
  backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(16px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(16px);
  border: 2px solid #1a8917;
  border-radius: 999px;
  box-shadow:
    0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9),
    0 8px 28px rgba(26, 137, 23, 0.22),
    0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Pretendard", sans-serif;
  max-width: calc(100vw - 24px);
}
.floating-nav a {
  flex: 1 1 auto;
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 5px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
  color: #4a4a4a;
  white-space: nowrap;
  min-height: 40px;
  transition: background 0.18s ease, color 0.18s ease, transform 0.12s;
}
.floating-nav a:active { transform: scale(0.95); }
.floating-nav a .cnt {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  min-width: 20px; height: 20px; padding: 0 6px;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800;
  color: #6b6b6b;
  font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
}
.floating-nav a.active {
  background: #1a8917; color: #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(26, 137, 23, 0.35);
}
.floating-nav a.active .cnt {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  color: #d9f99d;
}

@media (min-width: 640px) {
  .floating-nav a { padding: 10px 18px; font-size: 14px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

{# 중요도 → 색상 class 매핑 매크로 #}
{% macro score_class(sc) -%}
{%- if sc >= 9 -%}score-vhigh
{%- elif sc >= 8.5 -%}score-superhigh
{%- elif sc >= 8 -%}score-high
{%- elif sc >= 7 -%}score-midhigh
{%- elif sc >= 5 -%}score-mid
{%- elif sc >= 3 -%}score-low
{%- else -%}score-vlow
{%- endif -%}
{%- endmacro %}

{# 섹션 카운트 사전 계산 #}
{% set ns = namespace(ai_count=0, gen_count=0, all_count=0) %}
{% for sec in sections %}
  {% set ns.all_count = ns.all_count + sec.articles|length %}
  {% if 'AI' in sec.title %}{% set ns.ai_count = sec.articles|length %}{% endif %}
  {% if '종합' in sec.title %}{% set ns.gen_count = sec.articles|length %}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% set ai_count = ns.ai_count %}
{% set gen_count = ns.gen_count %}
{% set all_count = ns.all_count %}

{# ─────────────────────────────── 인사이트 블록 매크로 ─────────────────────────────── #}
{% macro render_insights(insights) -%}
{%- if insights -%}
<details class="why-insights" open>
  <summary>🧭 인사이트 보기</summary>
  {% if insights.ripple and insights.ripple.text %}
  <div class="axis" data-axis="ripple">
    <div class="axis-title">
      <span class="icon">{{ insights.ripple.icon or "📡" }}</span>
      <span>{{ insights.ripple.title }}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="axis-body">{{ insights.ripple.text }}</div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
  {% if insights.history and insights.history.text %}
  <div class="axis" data-axis="history">
    <div class="axis-title">
      <span class="icon">{{ insights.history.icon or "🗂" }}</span>
      <span>{{ insights.history.title }}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="axis-body">{{ insights.history.text }}</div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
  {% if insights.bonus %}
  {% for b in insights.bonus %}
  <div class="axis" data-axis="{{ b.type }}">
    <div class="axis-title">
      <span class="icon">{{ b.icon }}</span>
      <span>{{ b.title }}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="axis-body">{{ b.text }}</div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
  {% endif %}
</details>
{%- endif -%}
{%- endmacro %}

<div class="app">

  <header class="bar">
    <div class="brand">Daily Reader</div>
    <div class="edition">Vol. {{ issue_number }} · {{ period_label }}</div>
  </header>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="greeting">{{ hero_title_line1 }}</div>
    <h1>오늘의 {{ period_label }}<br>이야기</h1>
    <div class="sub">총 {{ all_count }}건 · 읽는 데 약 {{ (all_count * 0.5) | int }}분</div>
    <div class="meta">{{ generation_timestamp }} · Issue #{{ issue_number }}</div>
  </section>

  {% if trend_hashtags %}
  <div class="hashtags">
    {% for h in trend_hashtags %}<span>#{{ h }}</span>{% if not loop.last %} · {% endif %}{% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {# ══ 꼭 알아야 할 뉴스 섹션 ══ #}
  {% if must_know %}
  <section class="feed-sec must-read" id="sec-mustknow">
    {% set top = must_know[0] %}
    <article class="top-story">
      <div class="kicker">
        <span>⭐ Editor's Pick · {{ top.source }}</span>
        <span class="score {{ score_class(top.relevance_score) }}">{{ '%.1f' % top.relevance_score }}</span>
      </div>
      <h2>{{ top.title }}</h2>
      <div class="by">
        <span>By {{ top.source }}</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>{{ top.published_at_display }}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="body">{{ top.ai_summary }}</div>
      {% if top.keywords %}
      <div class="keywords">
        {% for kw in top.keywords %}<span># {{ kw }}</span>{% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
      {{ render_insights(top.insights) }}
    </article>

    {% if must_know|length > 1 %}
    <div class="sec-divider"><h2>꼭 알아야 할 뉴스</h2></div>
    {% for art in must_know[1:] %}
    <a class="story" href="{{ art.original_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <div class="head">
        <span class="src">{{ art.source }}</span>
        <span class="dot">·</span>
        <span>{{ art.published_at_display }}</span>
      </div>
      <h3>{{ art.title }}</h3>
      <p class="lede">{{ art.ai_summary[:180] }}{% if art.ai_summary|length > 180 %}…{% endif %}</p>
      {% if art.keywords %}
      <div class="keywords">
        {% for kw in art.keywords %}<span># {{ kw }}</span>{% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="foot">
        <div class="read">{{ (art.ai_summary|length / 200) | round | int + 1 }} min read</div>
        <div class="score {{ score_class(art.relevance_score) }}">{{ '%.1f' % art.relevance_score }}</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
    {% endif %}
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  {# ══ 카테고리별 섹션 — AI 뉴스 / 종합 뉴스 ══ #}
  {% for sec in sections %}
  {% if sec.articles %}
  {% set sid = 'sec-ai' if 'AI' in sec.title else 'sec-general' %}
  <section class="feed-sec" id="{{ sid }}">
    <div class="sec-divider"><h2>{{ sec.title }}</h2></div>
    {% for art in sec.articles %}
    <a class="story" href="{{ art.original_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <div class="head">
        <span class="src">{{ art.source }}</span>
        <span class="dot">·</span>
        <span>{{ art.published_at_display }}</span>
      </div>
      <h3>{{ art.title }}</h3>
      <p class="lede">{{ art.ai_summary[:150] }}{% if art.ai_summary|length > 150 %}…{% endif %}</p>
      {% if art.keywords %}
      <div class="keywords">
        {% for kw in art.keywords %}<span># {{ kw }}</span>{% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="foot">
        <div class="read">{{ (art.ai_summary|length / 200) | round | int + 1 }} min read</div>
        <div class="score {{ score_class(art.relevance_score) }}">{{ '%.1f' % art.relevance_score }}</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
  {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}

  <footer>
    <div class="disclosure">본 리포트는 Claude Opus 4.7이 RSS 원문을 분석해 생성합니다. 사실관계는 각 원문에서 확인하세요.</div>
    <div class="issue">ISSUE #{{ issue_number }}</div>
    <div class="sources">
      {% for src in rss_sources %}{{ src }}{% if not loop.last %} · {% endif %}{% endfor %}
    </div>
  </footer>

</div>

{# ═══════════════ 플로팅 섹션 네비게이션 ═══════════════ #}
<nav class="floating-nav" aria-label="섹션 이동">
  <a href="#sec-mustknow" data-sec="sec-mustknow" class="active">
    <span>⭐</span>
    <span>꼭알아야</span>
    <span class="cnt">{{ must_know|length }}</span>
  </a>
  {% if ai_count > 0 %}
  <a href="#sec-ai" data-sec="sec-ai">
    <span>🤖</span>
    <span>AI뉴스</span>
    <span class="cnt">{{ ai_count }}</span>
  </a>
  {% endif %}
  {% if gen_count > 0 %}
  <a href="#sec-general" data-sec="sec-general">
    <span>📰</span>
    <span>종합뉴스</span>
    <span class="cnt">{{ gen_count }}</span>
  </a>
  {% endif %}
</nav>

<script>
(function(){
  var navLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.floating-nav a');
  var sections = Array.prototype.filter.call(
    document.querySelectorAll('.feed-sec'),
    function(s){ return s.id; }
  );
  if (!sections.length || !navLinks.length) return;

  function setActive(id){
    navLinks.forEach(function(a){
      a.classList.toggle('active', a.getAttribute('data-sec') === id);
    });
  }

  if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
    var io = new IntersectionObserver(function(entries){
      var visible = entries.filter(function(e){ return e.isIntersecting; });
      if (!visible.length) return;
      visible.sort(function(a,b){
        return a.target.getBoundingClientRect().top - b.target.getBoundingClientRect().top;
      });
      setActive(visible[0].target.id);
    }, { rootMargin: '-25% 0px -55% 0px', threshold: 0 });
    sections.forEach(function(s){ io.observe(s); });
  }

  navLinks.forEach(function(a){
    a.addEventListener('click', function(){
      setActive(a.getAttribute('data-sec'));
    });
  });
})();
</script>

</body>
</html>
